title: GoPro Awards: Surfing Tahiti With Leif Engstrom
description:
Join Leif Engstrom as he shows us just how good the waves are in Teahupo'o, Tahiti. Leif was awarded $5,000 for editing this video and submitting it to GoPro Awards. 

Shot 100% on the HERO4® camera 

Music
Silent Lions "Stolen In The Heat Of The Moment"
